Package GPS_Reader

The package consists of the classes which is related to the GPS and processes the information The package contains CoordinateProcessor.java : to process the coordinates and return the correct result, GpsConnector.java : to connect to the GPS by port and get the information, and NMEAProcessor.java : to process the information given by GpsConnector.java.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CoordinateProcessor The class contains the methods to work with coordinates and process them.
GpsConnector A class to connect to GPS-Device and receive the information as Strings.
NMEAProcessor This class provides methods in order to process four types of the sentences (GGA, GSA, GSV, and RMC) received by the GPS unit.
